  gCapsuleFeaturePkgTokenSpaceGuid.PcdTopSwapDisableSwSmi  ## CONSUMES
  gCapsuleFeaturePkgTokenSpaceGuid.PcdTopSwapSmiSupport    ## CONSUMES

[Protocols]
